lemma silent_move_into_silent_move2: assumes "s -\<tau>\<rightarrow> s'" shows "\<exists>tl. silent_move2 s tl s'"
using assms
proof(cases)
fix tl
assume "s -tl\<rightarrow> s'" "\<tau>move s tl s'"
thus "\<exists>tl. silent_move2 s tl s'"
unfolding silent_move2_def
by blast
qed
